{"page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Ideal Health Consultants Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Design Authority\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Ideal offers strategic change and technical expertise to ensure the design of your programme is created correctly, run well and delivers what it should, when it should. We use programme assurance tools and techniques to ensure the programme is correctly designed, well managed, and delivered to meet requirements.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Strategic change and technical expertise\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent authority to steer the programme correctly\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Highly experienced in delivering IT strategy in the healthcare environment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Guide and lead existing team members\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Programme assurance tools and techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support organisation vision and strategy development\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support and advice using best practice structured methods and techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support from early engagement, through all stages to project completion\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     We work exclusively in the healthcare sector\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ideal has supported 150 Trusts with their health systems projects\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Correctly designed and well managed programme, delivered to meet requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Your project team members understand their roles and programme goals\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance can be measured to manage risk\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Most appropriate resource in place using Ideal\u2019s Lifecycle Resource Model\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     High quality programme managers with extensive health systems implementation experience\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Wide breadth and depth of health systems experience\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     High value and quality in a single, proven, flexible approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent reviews act as a early and on-going warning mechanism\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risks  highlighted before they become issues and suitable interventions provided\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assess, measure, monitor, review and report progress throughout change programme\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3250 to \u00a3600 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92722/5468398817378304-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92722/5468398817378304-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92722/5468398817378304-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92722/5468398817378304-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5468\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      3988\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      1737\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      8304\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Ideal Health Consultants Limited\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Matthew Proffitt\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"telephone\">\n       01483 453508\n      </